name: Die Biene Maja: Klatschmohnwiese in Gefahr
Drive
description: VR Arcade Racing. Put your foot to the floor and hang on as you battle challenging opponents across a range of tracks and racing types in search of glorious victory. Built for VR it lets you feel the thrill of racing with beautiful car interiors and track environments.

name: Roland Garros French Open 2000
description:
This is a 3D Simulation Tennis game based on the famous Roland Garros franchise. 16 men and 16 women play on 8 different courts. You can choose Singles, Doubles or Mixed Doubles. Each win puts cash in your pocket towards rackets and games with more skilled players.

There are 3 game modes: Tournament, Exhibition, and Practice. In addition, there 12 rackets to unlock, 8 hidden players and 2 bonus courts, plus a 4-player multiplayer option.

name: Mavis Beacon Teaches Typing! for Kids
Elitserien 2001
description: "Elitserien 2001" is an expansion pack for the EA Sports game NHL 2001. It includes the Swedish Elitserien and the Finnish SM-liiga, the top hockey leagues in Sweden and Finland. The cover features Henrik Zetterberg, a player from Timrå (and later the Detroit Red Wings) in Sweden.

name: Pick Up
description: OK, here's the deal. If you want that lover of your dreams to get off their pedestal and go out with you, you need to present them with the right gifts. Then you can head over to the Love Nest Hotel to really score! You start with your lover of a pedestal on the left and various items floating above you. You must shoot each item once to acquire it. If an item starts flashing, shoot it next because after a short time, you'll lose a chance. If you shoot an item a second time, you will lose it and a chance. Lose all your chances and the game is over. If you collect all the items needed, head over to the pedestal then head off the screen to the right. Head to the door of the hotel and the hotel sign will say how many times you have scored. Now head left to start the next level.

name: Comanche CD
description: Comanche CD is an enhanced version of the helicopter combat simulator Comanche: Maximum Overkill. This CD-ROM release expands on the original game, likely offering improved graphics, additional missions, and enhanced audio capabilities made possible by the increased storage capacity of CD media. Players pilot the RAH-66 Comanche attack helicopter through various combat scenarios, utilizing NovaLogic's Voxel engine to render detailed, lifelike terrain. The game maintains the accessible flight model and intense combat of its predecessor, focusing on engaging gameplay over strict simulation. Comanche CD probably includes the original campaign missions along with new content, providing both new and returning players with an expanded helicopter combat experience that showcases the technical advancements of CD-ROM gaming technology.

name: Robot
description: Robot is a hack (variant) of Gallagant.

name: Mad Cars
description:
This year the cars have all gone mad.
Steer a bunch of cars on a highway without rules and try not to crash them, at least not all of them.
Fill the road with your hoard of cars and complete the fun levels. You'll be dodging rocks, pipes, holes in the road, trucks and many more, that will send chunks of your hoard of cars flying and explode.

name: Soccer RPG: Become the coach for the national team!
Inside Trader: The Authentic Stock Trading Game
Lab Rat
description: This satirical adventure stars a metrics-obsessed AI who will monitor, profile, and entertain you as you progress through over a hundred genre-bending puzzles.

name: Comanche: Maximum Overkill - Mission Disk 1
description: Comanche: Maximum Overkill - Mission Disk 1 is an expansion for the helicopter combat simulation game Comanche: Maximum Overkill. This add-on content extends the original game with new missions and scenarios for players to tackle. The game puts players in control of the RAH-66 Comanche helicopter, a stealth attack helicopter. Players engage in combat missions, utilizing the Comanche's advanced weaponry and stealth capabilities to complete objectives. The expansion likely introduces new environments, enemy types, and mission structures to provide fresh challenges for players who completed the base game. As a mission disk, it focuses on expanding gameplay content rather than introducing significant new features or mechanics. Comanche: Maximum Overkill - Mission Disk 1 aims to provide additional content for fans of the original game, offering more opportunities to experience the game's blend of realistic helicopter simulation and action-packed combat scenarios.

name: Haven & Hearth
description:
Haven & Hearth is a MMORPG (Massive Multiplayer Online Roleplaying Game) set in a fictional world loosely inspired by Slavic and Germanic myth and legend.

The game sets itself apart from other games in the genre in its aim to provide players with an interactive, affectable and mutable game world, which can be permanently and fundamentally changed and affected through actions undertaken by the players.

Our fundamental goal with Haven & Hearth is to create a game in which player choices have permanent and/or lasting effects and, thus, providing said players with a meaningful and fun gaming experience

name: Maximum Surge
description: Maximum Surge is a cancelled video game planned for release in 1996 that would have featured full-motion video starred Walter Koenig and Yasmine Bleeth.

name: WtBoy
description: A little game about a little man who needs to get out of a big terrible place.

name: Saints Row: The Third - Enter the Dominatrix
description:
Saints Row: The Third - Enter the Dominatrix would've been a DLC similar to saint row IV. The player would've been sent to a virtual world and get superpowers. The DLC was cancelled and fused with the next instalment of the franchise.
The original release date would've been September 2012.

name: RunPostmanRun
description: A steampunk style, game in which its main character, a Postman, runs along Victorian streets delivering letters into the citizen's mailboxes.

name: Table Soccer
description: Bring your own football stadium to life and take the beautiful game anywhere you go.

name: TV School House II: Math Fun
Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet - Premium Edition
description:
Get the full SWORD ART ONLINE: FATAL BULLET experience with the Complete Edition which includes the main game, three DLC packs, the "Dissonance of the Nexus" Expansion, and bonus in-game items!

Your choices are heavier and faster than a bullet.

name: Avoid Droid
description: Stay out of the way in this wacky fruit collecting game.

name: Majestic-12
description: A game about weird little people defending the universe. Aside from being incredibly stupid-fun, Majestic-12 is a 3d action side-scroller where you take control of an elite MJ-12 commando and battle your way through secret installations and strange alien environments with your friends.

name: Sam & Max: Freelance Police
description: A canceled follow-up to the LucasArts adventure game. Sam & Max Hit the Road. It was announced in 2002 and cancelled in 2004, due to LucasArts' concerns that an adventure game for the PC would not be profitable at that time.

name: Dark Parables: The Little Mermaid and the Purple Tide HD
Small Town Terrors: Galdor's Bluff HD
Blissfull
description:
Blissfull is a tribute to Sudoku cubes. It's a love letter to all Rubik's cube style puzzles; re-imagined in a 2D world and made with love. It's a relaxed puzzler about unlocking happiness.
60 thoughtfully designed and curated levels await you, where you restore euphoria by rearranging numbered locks into their correct positions.

name: Gold Game for Who's Your Daddy
Hunter Willie Hunting Wild Safari Dinosaurs
Reflections of Life: Tree of Dreams
Undead vs. Plants War - Fun Ricochet Shooter
Railworks Class56 DLC
description: Ever dreamed of driving trains? Now you can! Train Simulator 2018 brings to life some amazing train challenges on real world routes and delivers the ultimate railway hobby.

name: Edge of Reality: Ring of Destiny
Crash Club
description:
Crash Club is massively multiplayer action with over 30 players live and real time in every game. Everything can be crashed, with weapons and abilities to battle other drivers available right in the middle of the action.
Over 25 unique car makes and countless model varieties, with infinite paint, decal, accessory and emoji options. Manage your garage and sell old rides to make way for better vehicles. Pimp them out with upgrades and powers to define your unique style and get the upper hand!
This is Crash Club - a living, breathing world from Prettygreat to take online mobile multiplayer to new heights!

Bouncy Ball: The Impossible Tile Game

description: Prim Rogue is a randomly generated action-RPG with Rogue-like elements. Three unique classes, an interesting system of character development, a lot of strong enemies - all this you will find here!

name: Lost In Space 2
description: Minimalistic sci-fi running game with lots of achievements.

name: Before the Blood
description: Before the Blood is an intense 3rd-person urban beat-em-up in which you punch, kick and knock out rival gang members on you journey to uncover the truth at Hilden Green - the place where Micky's brother, Dean, allegedly took his own life.

name: Slug Slasher
description: Save the world from an onslaught of giant slugs in Slug Slasher! Using only your trusty bucket of salt, smash, dash, and slash through ridiculous enemies and crazy bosses as you fight your way to the slugs' homeland.

name: Lunar Soil
description:
Your interstellar career is now within reach!
Lunar Soil is a 3rd person moon-based management game about you, your AI crew and your corporate sponsorship.

name: Gl1tch
description: Gl1tch shrinks you down to a bit and sends you into circuits to overload and disable them by utilizing arcade-style controls and smart-thinking strategy.

name: Endless Fun: The Battle for Peanuts
description: You're a young bandit. To become a tough bandit you have to break the law. Do the tasks and do not fall into the hands of the police.

name: Empire of the Dead Souls
description: Empire of the Dead Souls - it's tower defence with elements of clicker, in which you need to defend your shrine from various dead souls, that are more than 1000 years old. Don't let monsters to destroy your shrine by killing them. With each level of the soul begin to move faster, also each new level you will meet new souls and at the last level you need to beat the boss.

name: Night Sky
description: Play with up to three friends and look for all nine of Lucifer's trophies; Limbo, Lust, Gluttony, Greed, Wrath, Heresy, Violence, Fraud and Treachery. Find these trophies while getting chased down by Lucifer in order to win! Offers you many different maps to immerse yourself in.

name: Segment
description: SEGMENT - it's a platform 2D shooter, whose actions occur in the near post-apocalyptic future.

name: Maze of Infection
description: A survival-Top down shooter full of zombies!

name: Ana: The Game
description:
If you answer that unknown number, you’re screwed... 
Are you willing to risk everything … ?

name: Death from Unknown: Survival
description: Once a beautiful island, now a deadly trap. You will have to use all your available gear, along with your building skills to survive the deadly night of this place. You can try to survive alone or team up with friends.

name: The Time Machine - Trapped in time
Scrambled Galaxy
description: Dynamic online battles in real time with elements of strategy and cards game. Collect and improve cards of effects, turrets and intergalactic pirates: robots, aliens, monsters, insects and other extraterrestrial creatures.

name: Zombie Grenades Practice
description:
What could be better than the taste of victory? Only humanity's victory over the zombie.
Zombie Grenades Practice VR is a game that prepares you for a zombie apocalypse. Imagine that you are out of ammo but you have grenades. Their number is limited and you are heavily outnumbered by zombies, so you should think carefully before each throw. Good luck!

name: Afraid Project
description: What you do in the game becomes reality!

name: Super Spy Girl Salon: Spa, Makeup and Dressup Game
The Crew 2: Motor Edition
description:
Rule the road, dominate the sea & tear up the sky with The Crew 2: Motor Edition.

The Motor Edition includes:
- The Crew 2: SteelBook Gold Edition, including the Season Pass and a collectible SteelBook case.
- A 11.81" x 5.9" specialty license plate customized to reflect the spirit of The Crew 2.
- A 25" x 20" fold out road map of the game - your guide to explore the entire USA, full of activities and hidden surprises.
- Four motorsport stickers - choose your own style between the 4 Motornation families.
- High quality Collector Box packaging
- Three days early access.
- The Crew 2 Motorsports Deluxe Pack
- Ford F-15- Raptor Race Truck 2017
- Abarth 500 2008 Monster Truck Edition
- Pilatus PC-21.
- Three outfits to customize your avatar

name: G1 Jockey 4 2008
description: Horse racing simulators are geared towards an incredibly narrow niche market. Aspiring jockeys who also have a passion for console gaming are a rare breed, so Koei’s biggest challenge with G1 Jockey 4 2008 is convincing the wider audience to saddle up. Skipping those tedious tutorials and diving straight in is always tempting, but in this case inadvisable. The training section is reasonably comprehensive and essential to anyone actually wanting to progress with this one. Care is taken to introduce the player to every aspect of the game, but there is great deal of information to absorb both on an off the track. Constant reference to that instruction manual is inevitable when you start off on the long arduous journey that is story mode.

name: Luc Bernard's Reaper
description: Colourful action game for PS Vita.

name: Pro Pilkki 2
description: The original ice fishing simulator published in 2013.

name: Kajko i Kokosz: W Krainie Borostworów
Blobster
description:
Get ready to meet one gooey hero…
Blobtopia is at risk from some nasty pollution from the evil Big and Powerful Corporation, and it’s up to you to help! Blobster is an awesome platforming adventure with a twist! Flick the flubbery fella across incredible levels; avoid pitfalls, water hazards, squish pesky bad guys and collect amazing power-ups on your way to cleaning up Blobtopia and defeating Blobzilla!

name: Soccerholix
description: Rule the world and beyond with your almighty soccer skills.

name: WSOP
description:
Show off your Texas Hold'em Poker skills!

The Official World Series of Poker App.

name: The Sewer Goblet: The Wu-Tang Clan and the Wu-Tang Baby
description:
It was an ordinary day at the Wu-Tang mansion. Ghostface and Raekwon tossed around a football in the backyard while Ol’ Dirty Bastard, RZA, and the rest of the gang watched the game inside. What nobody expected was the knock at the door that would forever change their lives.

Much to their surprise, a tiny but majestic baby with a mysterious pendant was on their doorstep and with nowhere else to go and no sign of who the baby belonged to, the Wu-Tang Clan had no choice but to adopt the tot and nickname him the Wu-Tang Baby.

Little did they know, this baby was much sought after by an eldritch wizard living in the sewers for his pendant, and when the baby was kidnapped by the Cheese Panda XD, a henchman of the wizard, the Wu-Tang Clan was tasked with finding the wizard’s lair in the sewers and rescuing the kidnapped baby from his evil clutches in Tales of Game’s Studios Presents The Sewer Goblet: The Wu-Tang Clan and the Wu-Tang Baby!

name: No, Human
description: “No, Human” is a physics based action-puzzle game, taking place during the latest conflict between mankind's puny struggle for meaning and the universe. With your skillful finger, a delight in destruction and some patience, you will demobilize the human presence outside of planet earth in a joyful way.

name: Pokémon Fushigi no Dungeon: Ikuzo! Arashi/Mezase! Hikari/Susume! Honoo no Boukendan
The Black Hole
description: The Black Hole is a TPS with puzzle solving elements. You'll play as a secret agent in the Black Hole Agency. Defeat enemies with your gun and solve puzzles. Collect mysterious items in the levels and survive a conspiracy.

name: Taekwondo
description: Discover the joy of kicking a friend’s butt and prove your worth as a taekwondo fighter in The Taekwondo Game – Global Tournament, the first ever mobile taekwondo game. Based on authentic motion-captured taekwondo movements and Olympic rules, it’s as near the real thing as you can come.

name: The Game of Life: DX Jinsei Game
Soccer Team Manager: English and Italian Leagues
